1
00:01:40,980 --> 00:01:51,060
Today we are worshipping Adi Shakti.

2
00:01:52,140 --> 00:02:00,180
I think this is the most important puja

3
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:09,380
because it is the power of Adi Shakti

4
00:02:09,540 --> 00:02:13,460
that has given you Self Realisation,

5
00:02:13,940 --> 00:02:17,340
that has given you the Truth,

6
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:23,460
that has given you the power of compassion and love.

7
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:45,540
That's the power that separated from Sadashiva

8
00:02:47,820 --> 00:03:05,780
and this power wanted Herself to create this complete universe.

9
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:16,220
Universes after universes, She's creating and loving.

10
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:24,660
With Her love, She did this great creation,

11
00:03:24,820 --> 00:03:30,180
creation of this world also.

12
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:36,780
This is a specially selected planet,

13
00:03:36,940 --> 00:03:43,540
which was very beautifully brought in the centre

14
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:47,140
between the sun and the moon

15
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:56,500
for the creation of, ultimately, the human beings.

16
00:03:58,460 --> 00:04:09,820
This is Her great work with such love and affection

17
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:13,780
and with very great hope

18
00:04:15,260 --> 00:04:22,980
that Her children will know the truth

19
00:04:23,460 --> 00:04:27,820
and will get the ultimate knowledge about themselves

20
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:32,100
and about everything else.

21
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:42,620
As you have read in the Bible

22
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:49,420
about how Adi Shakti came in the form of a snake

23
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:52,780
and told human beings

24
00:04:52,940 --> 00:05:01,860
that you have to know the knowledge,

25
00:05:02,020 --> 00:05:08,220
Adam and Eve, and to Eve specially,

26
00:05:08,383 --> 00:05:15,060
and they accepted to eat the fruit of knowledge

27
00:05:18,170 --> 00:05:23,050
because they would have remained just like animals,

28
00:05:23,210 --> 00:05:27,010
without knowing anything subtleties of life —

29
00:05:27,170 --> 00:05:30,770
little higher animals maybe —

30
00:05:32,490 --> 00:05:39,290
that once they ate the fruit they started feeling

31
00:05:39,970 --> 00:05:43,210
that there is something wrong the

32
00:05:43,370 --> 00:05:47,330
way they are without any clothes,

33
00:05:47,850 --> 00:05:52,850
so they brought some leaves of the tree

34
00:05:53,010 --> 00:05:56,450
and covered themselves.

35
00:05:56,970 --> 00:06:03,850
So the first knowledge came was of chastity

36
00:06:04,730 --> 00:06:10,210
because Shri Ganesha was established

37
00:06:10,410 --> 00:06:18,370
and His influence brought forth this consciousness

38
00:06:18,530 --> 00:06:21,450
that we have to cover our bodies.

39
00:06:21,610 --> 00:06:25,010
We are no more animals.

40
00:06:25,170 --> 00:06:29,130
Only the animals

41
00:06:29,290 --> 00:06:31,970
— of course, they're not standing, so it is all right —

42
00:06:32,130 --> 00:06:35,130
are not aware of it.

43
00:06:38,770 --> 00:06:44,090
With the knowledge of chastity,

44
00:06:44,250 --> 00:06:48,410
gradually human beings started growing

45
00:06:48,890 --> 00:06:53,130
into beautiful nations,

46
00:06:54,810 --> 00:07:01,410
but there are so many things, which were still to be known,

47
00:07:02,930 --> 00:07:05,810
to be aware of it.

48
00:07:06,810 --> 00:07:14,490
You may be aware of many things,

49
00:07:18,010 --> 00:07:27,930
but unless and until you get your spiritual awakening,

50
00:07:28,970 --> 00:07:33,570
unless and until you get your self knowledge,

51
00:07:33,730 --> 00:07:40,050
all other knowledge is absolutely nothing.

52
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:49,770
With this self knowledge only, you become powerful.

53
00:07:49,930 --> 00:07:57,490
The real power — the real power is of love and compassion.

54
00:08:00,650 --> 00:08:08,970
Today when you see the whole world is busy fighting

55
00:08:09,130 --> 00:08:14,810
and they are trying to protect people

56
00:08:14,970 --> 00:08:19,730
from wars and creating

57
00:08:19,890 --> 00:08:28,370
great, huge, protecting instruments.

58
00:08:29,650 --> 00:08:34,610
The whole world seems to be in a mad race

59
00:08:34,770 --> 00:08:40,690
of killing each other, of destroying each other,

60
00:08:40,850 --> 00:08:49,810
of competition, ambition,

61
00:08:49,970 --> 00:08:55,330
leading to fighting and then to greater wars.

62
00:08:55,610 --> 00:09:01,170
They're fighting for a piece of land.

63
00:09:02,130 --> 00:09:05,490
So ignorant they are.

64
00:09:05,650 --> 00:09:14,330
Can you carry even a pinch of this land with you

65
00:09:14,490 --> 00:09:17,130
when you die?

66
00:09:19,410 --> 00:09:23,370
When you are born you come with closed fists.

67
00:09:23,530 --> 00:09:28,570
When you die you go with open hands.

68
00:09:29,130 --> 00:09:32,730
What do you take with you?

69
00:09:32,890 --> 00:09:37,690
All right, you may not like to take anything,

70
00:09:37,850 --> 00:09:42,090
but do you enjoy whatever you think is so great

71
00:09:42,250 --> 00:09:45,530
for which you are fighting?

72
00:09:46,250 --> 00:09:53,090
Why this fighting going on among all nonsensical people?

73
00:09:53,930 --> 00:10:03,250
It's surprising how people give up their peace,

74
00:10:03,410 --> 00:10:06,490
give up their understanding

75
00:10:06,650 --> 00:10:12,250
when it comes to a piece of land.

76
00:10:15,850 --> 00:10:22,090
And the whole thing has moved into a very wrong direction

77
00:10:22,250 --> 00:10:28,530
and going towards complete destruction.

78
00:10:29,530 --> 00:10:39,450
The thing that has made human beings so much suffering

79
00:10:39,610 --> 00:10:47,570
because of all their ignorance,

80
00:10:47,730 --> 00:10:54,010
by which they have all those habits,

81
00:10:54,170 --> 00:10:57,850
all those attractions,

82
00:10:58,010 --> 00:11:04,610
all those identification, which is ruinous,

83
00:11:04,770 --> 00:11:12,330
which will ruin all of them, each one by one.

84
00:11:14,410 --> 00:11:16,930
They have to take to sense

85
00:11:17,090 --> 00:11:24,370
and they have to take to their self knowledge.

86
00:11:24,530 --> 00:11:33,010
Self knowledge is the key

87
00:11:34,010 --> 00:11:41,290
for a saviour to give to people.

88
00:11:43,170 --> 00:11:46,970
We have had so many saints.

89
00:11:47,130 --> 00:11:51,250
We have had so many Sufis.

90
00:11:51,410 --> 00:11:55,970
We had Tao people. We had Zen people.

91
00:11:56,130 --> 00:12:02,210
All kinds of realised souls came on this Earth.

92
00:12:03,210 --> 00:12:09,170
They all suffered. They were tortured. Nobody understood them.

93
00:12:10,610 --> 00:12:18,170
But now the time has come for you to know the truth,

94
00:12:18,650 --> 00:12:25,210
but truth which is not dry, truth which has compassion,

95
00:12:25,370 --> 00:12:29,370
truth that encompasses everyone,

96
00:12:29,530 --> 00:12:37,730
that brings the complete view of our existence.

97
00:12:37,890 --> 00:12:44,370
Why are we here on this Earth? What is our purpose?

98
00:12:44,530 --> 00:12:47,490
What should we do? Adi Shakti's

99
00:12:48,730 --> 00:12:52,890
powers are such

100
00:12:53,050 --> 00:12:56,650
of love and compassion,

101
00:12:56,810 --> 00:13:02,010
that makes you understand your self first.

102
00:13:03,170 --> 00:13:09,450
The love, for you, is very, very limited.

103
00:13:10,010 --> 00:13:17,130
There's no awareness of your own being.

104
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:22,250
Just imagine what a great task is for you,

105
00:13:22,810 --> 00:13:28,410
how much you have to be seriously

106
00:13:28,570 --> 00:13:33,250
becoming aware of your self first.

107
00:13:34,290 --> 00:13:38,050
That is extremely important.

108
00:13:38,730 --> 00:13:43,330
First you have to be aware of your self.

109
00:13:45,490 --> 00:13:49,690
And now you have the light of your spirit.

110
00:13:49,850 --> 00:13:54,610
In the light of that spirit you can see what you are

111
00:13:54,930 --> 00:13:58,410
and you can see how far you are going,

112
00:13:58,570 --> 00:14:02,210
how wrong things you are doing,

113
00:14:02,370 --> 00:14:06,730
what harm you are doing to yourself

114
00:14:07,610 --> 00:14:11,250
and you have a power to cure it,

115
00:14:11,410 --> 00:14:16,610
to improve it and to come to your senses.

116
00:14:16,770 --> 00:14:21,170
These are the most important times.

117
00:14:21,330 --> 00:14:24,490
You will never get these times again.

118
00:14:24,650 --> 00:14:31,450
Never had it in the history and you can never get it in the future.

119
00:14:32,410 --> 00:14:39,370
This is the time you have got, not only the awareness,

120
00:14:39,530 --> 00:14:43,610
not only the self knowledge,

121
00:14:43,770 --> 00:14:47,810
but you know how to do it.

122
00:14:48,210 --> 00:14:51,330
Otherwise, about the saints,

123
00:14:51,490 --> 00:14:56,010
about those people, Tao and Zen people,

124
00:14:56,170 --> 00:14:58,850
they have just described

125
00:14:59,010 --> 00:15:05,770
what a person with self knowledge is,

126
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:10,970
how he behaves, how his style is,

127
00:15:11,130 --> 00:15:14,130
how he's so different from others.

128
00:15:14,290 --> 00:15:19,330
But none of them have said how you become that.

129
00:15:20,330 --> 00:15:23,970
No one has been able to say that.

130
00:15:24,130 --> 00:15:28,130
Nobody has been able to do that also

131
00:15:28,290 --> 00:15:36,730
because perhaps most of them didn't know about kundalini

132
00:15:36,970 --> 00:15:44,090
and those who knew also could not talk about it to people.

133
00:15:44,930 --> 00:15:50,330
So the greatest work of the Adi Shakti is

134
00:15:50,490 --> 00:15:59,770
to put the kundalini in your sacrum bone.

135
00:16:01,890 --> 00:16:08,290
This kundalini is not the Adi Shakti.

136
00:16:08,450 --> 00:16:12,010
The Adi Shakti is a much greater thing, a much bigger thing,

137
00:16:12,170 --> 00:16:17,490
much wider thing, much deeper, much stronger,

138
00:16:17,690 --> 00:16:20,930
much stronger, much more powerful.

139
00:16:21,090 --> 00:16:28,770
Kundalini is the reflection of Adi Shakti power

140
00:16:29,930 --> 00:16:36,210
and when She rises you know what happens to you

141
00:16:36,650 --> 00:16:42,450
and how you get your Realisation.

142
00:16:43,650 --> 00:16:47,410
But you have to be very watchful.

143
00:16:47,650 --> 00:16:52,410
Are you really a compassionate person?

144
00:16:54,130 --> 00:16:56,970
If you are compassionate,

145
00:16:57,130 --> 00:17:00,650
the first thing that will happen to any compassionate person,

146
00:17:00,810 --> 00:17:07,530
I think, will be to help others,

147
00:17:07,690 --> 00:17:10,450
to emancipate others.

148
00:17:10,610 --> 00:17:16,930
They cannot be satisfied with their own achievements

149
00:17:17,090 --> 00:17:26,130
and with their own state of Self Realisation.

150
00:17:26,290 --> 00:17:28,730
It cannot happen.

151
00:17:29,170 --> 00:17:35,210
What was the need for the Adi Shakti to do all, all these efforts

152
00:17:35,370 --> 00:17:37,050
to work so hard?

153
00:17:37,210 --> 00:17:42,210
You know that, that I had to work very, very hard,

154
00:17:42,370 --> 00:17:45,850
but, from my very childhood

155
00:17:46,490 --> 00:17:49,410
I've worked very hard

156
00:17:49,570 --> 00:17:54,850
and I've gone through very difficult times,

157
00:17:55,010 --> 00:18:01,890
very, very difficult times according to human understanding,

158
00:18:02,050 --> 00:18:08,050
but the worst time I have, when I see

159
00:18:08,210 --> 00:18:12,450
those people whom I have given Realisation,

160
00:18:12,610 --> 00:18:16,570
those who are self-realised people,

161
00:18:16,730 --> 00:18:24,370
they are the ones who have no responsibility for others

162
00:18:24,530 --> 00:18:28,410
and, if they have, it is very little.

163
00:18:28,570 --> 00:18:31,730
They don't have that compassion

164
00:18:31,890 --> 00:18:34,770
and don't have that love

165
00:18:34,930 --> 00:18:38,610
that we have to today save the world,

166
00:18:38,770 --> 00:18:41,010
save the humanity.

167
00:18:41,170 --> 00:18:47,410
That's our — not only our principal work,

168
00:18:47,570 --> 00:18:52,410
but the only work that we have to do.

169
00:18:52,570 --> 00:18:57,930
All other things are going to achieve nothing,

170
00:18:58,090 --> 00:19:03,850
except for your own efforts here,

171
00:19:04,010 --> 00:19:06,690
individual efforts

172
00:19:06,850 --> 00:19:10,170
to give Self Realisation to others

173
00:19:10,330 --> 00:19:14,170
and give them this knowledge.

174
00:19:14,330 --> 00:19:20,210
This knowledge is so, so easy to understand.

175
00:19:20,370 --> 00:19:23,850
It is very subtle, no doubt,

176
00:19:24,010 --> 00:19:26,770
and, as I've told you,

177
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:33,130
that the quantum theory they're talking about now, the scientists,

178
00:19:33,290 --> 00:19:39,210
is that they have seen those miraculous waves of lights

179
00:19:39,370 --> 00:19:44,490
and they are trying to find out something about it.

180
00:19:44,650 --> 00:19:51,690
It cannot be that some Sahaja Yogis will rise above others.

181
00:19:51,850 --> 00:19:58,970
Every one of you [has] to know that this is a very special thing

182
00:19:59,130 --> 00:20:02,210
that has happened to you.

183
00:20:02,370 --> 00:20:04,930
Even if you had gone to Himalayas,

184
00:20:05,090 --> 00:20:07,650
even if you have starved yourself,

185
00:20:07,810 --> 00:20:14,130
even if you have been singing the praise of God for years,

186
00:20:14,290 --> 00:20:21,010
even you had done all kinds of rituals and penances,

187
00:20:21,170 --> 00:20:23,970
you could not have got your Realisation.

188
00:20:24,130 --> 00:20:26,570
That would not have been possible.

189
00:20:26,730 --> 00:20:33,210
I knew this. That's why I have to work very hard,

190
00:20:33,370 --> 00:20:38,970
facing all kinds of problems, all kinds of turmoils,

191
00:20:39,130 --> 00:20:44,530
all kinds of pressures, what was the thing?

192
00:20:44,690 --> 00:20:51,530
Just to see that you all are created

193
00:20:51,690 --> 00:20:54,810
and you're all My hands.

194
00:20:54,970 --> 00:21:00,770
You have to work. Every finger has to work.

195
00:21:00,930 --> 00:21:03,770
And that is what I have been telling you,

196
00:21:03,930 --> 00:21:11,290
that now it is our responsibility to see that we become,

197
00:21:11,450 --> 00:21:18,450
not only Sahaja Yogis ourself, but blossoming time

198
00:21:18,690 --> 00:21:24,410
and many, many Sahaja Yogis we should have.

199
00:21:26,010 --> 00:21:30,690
It's a work of Adi Shakti.

200
00:21:30,850 --> 00:21:33,570
Try to understand this.

201
00:21:33,730 --> 00:21:37,530
It's not work of any saint.

202
00:21:37,690 --> 00:21:42,290
It's not work of any incarnation.

203
00:21:42,450 --> 00:21:46,330
It's not work of any politician.

204
00:21:46,490 --> 00:21:52,770
And not work of any big leader.

205
00:21:52,930 --> 00:21:56,970
It is the work of Adi Shakti,

206
00:21:57,170 --> 00:22:04,330
which is so transparently showing its results in you.

207
00:22:04,490 --> 00:22:10,370
Now it is for you to see.

208
00:22:11,850 --> 00:22:18,770
To please Me is your ardent desire, I know.

209
00:22:18,930 --> 00:22:28,450
I see how you love Me and how you want to do for Me.

210
00:22:28,610 --> 00:22:32,530
The greatest thing you can do for Me

211
00:22:32,690 --> 00:22:36,970
is to spread Sahaja Yoga.

212
00:22:37,530 --> 00:22:45,210
It is a very special, extremely difficult blessings you have got.

213
00:22:47,970 --> 00:22:51,410
You didn't have to do any efforts.

214
00:22:51,570 --> 00:22:55,650
You didn't have to pay any money.

215
00:22:56,450 --> 00:23:04,570
You don't have to get sick with rituals.

216
00:23:04,730 --> 00:23:08,770
You got it spontaneously.

217
00:23:09,730 --> 00:23:15,330
But that doesn't mean that it's sort of your birthright to get it.

218
00:23:15,490 --> 00:23:19,530
[It] is the work of Adi Shakti.

219
00:23:22,050 --> 00:23:31,770
And the work of Adi Shakti has to be shown in your life.

220
00:23:33,530 --> 00:23:41,810
[It] is the compassion, without any reward.

221
00:23:42,570 --> 00:23:45,890
People have tried to spread their religion

222
00:23:46,050 --> 00:23:49,730
by showing compassion to poor people,

223
00:23:49,890 --> 00:23:54,850
looking after the poor people, handicapped people.

224
00:23:55,930 --> 00:24:02,450
There's no need, actually, for Sahaja Yogis to do that.

225
00:24:03,570 --> 00:24:08,770
What they have to do is to transform other people.

226
00:24:09,050 --> 00:24:14,210
Find out ways and methods how you can transform,

227
00:24:14,530 --> 00:24:19,170
how you can spread the message of Adi Shakti.

228
00:24:19,530 --> 00:24:21,810
Put your mind to it

229
00:24:21,970 --> 00:24:26,490
and you will know how you can manage it.

230
00:24:29,970 --> 00:24:37,050
There should be all the time compelling desire

231
00:24:37,210 --> 00:24:40,050
that we have to find out method

232
00:24:40,210 --> 00:24:44,010
by which we can spread Sahaja Yoga.

233
00:24:44,930 --> 00:24:51,210
Otherwise it's like what Christ has described

234
00:24:51,370 --> 00:24:58,330
that some seed fell on the marshy land

235
00:24:58,890 --> 00:25:04,810
and they sprouted, but never grew.

236
00:25:05,130 --> 00:25:12,250
You can only grow in the real sense of the word

237
00:25:12,890 --> 00:25:19,170
and become something very, very special and real

238
00:25:20,130 --> 00:25:26,130
by knowing what you can do.

239
00:25:27,370 --> 00:25:30,370
I have a vision, no doubt,

240
00:25:30,530 --> 00:25:34,730
and I've been talking about it quite a lot,

241
00:25:35,010 --> 00:25:41,370
but it ends up with the puja is not a good thing.

242
00:25:42,170 --> 00:25:46,410
I know some countries are very difficult.

243
00:25:46,570 --> 00:25:50,650
Try to find out what is the problem,

244
00:25:50,810 --> 00:25:55,770
why it is so very difficult.

245
00:25:56,770 --> 00:26:02,010
Attention has to be paid to this,

246
00:26:02,170 --> 00:26:09,770
that what other human beings are doing to destroy themselves,

247
00:26:11,210 --> 00:26:14,450
as if it is the part and parcel of the same game

248
00:26:14,610 --> 00:26:19,370
which we call as the last judgement,

249
00:26:19,530 --> 00:26:23,210
but let us, through our compassion and love,

250
00:26:23,370 --> 00:26:26,330
save as many as possible.

251
00:26:27,850 --> 00:26:31,850
This is the work of Adi Shakti,

252
00:26:32,410 --> 00:26:37,250
not the work of any saint or any incarnation.

253
00:26:37,410 --> 00:26:40,010
They're all there, no doubt.

254
00:26:40,170 --> 00:26:45,090
They're all with us, all the time to help us,

255
00:26:45,250 --> 00:26:49,850
but you people have the power of Adi Shakti,

256
00:26:50,250 --> 00:26:53,690
which is very great,

257
00:26:53,850 --> 00:26:57,650
which is very penetrating,

258
00:26:57,810 --> 00:27:00,850
which is miraculous.

259
00:27:01,010 --> 00:27:04,290
It's so effective,

260
00:27:04,450 --> 00:27:10,410
but unless and until you become aware of your own powers,

261
00:27:10,570 --> 00:27:13,570
how will you work it out.

262
00:27:13,730 --> 00:27:19,130
It would be like a dead machine that has everything,

263
00:27:19,290 --> 00:27:23,490
but nobody is there to work it out.

264
00:27:23,690 --> 00:27:30,530
All the time I had to go through very,

265
00:27:30,690 --> 00:27:33,610
very hazardous times

266
00:27:33,770 --> 00:27:40,530
and sometimes I felt that I may have to take another birth,

267
00:27:40,690 --> 00:27:44,610
the way things are so difficult for Me.

268
00:27:44,770 --> 00:27:51,250
But now, for you, it has been very easy,

269
00:27:52,170 --> 00:27:57,370
as if the one who makes the road has to work very hard,

270
00:27:57,530 --> 00:27:59,970
but those who walk on that,

271
00:28:00,130 --> 00:28:05,290
they don't realise how easily they have got it.

272
00:28:05,450 --> 00:28:11,730
And if they realise this, then they will realise also

273
00:28:11,890 --> 00:28:14,890
'Let many walk on this road,

274
00:28:15,050 --> 00:28:17,570
which was created with such

275
00:28:17,730 --> 00:28:21,850
patience, understanding and love.'

276
00:28:22,010 --> 00:28:28,610
I have to really see you all Sahaja Yogis

277
00:28:28,770 --> 00:28:34,250
doing your level best to change this world

278
00:28:34,410 --> 00:28:36,410
— has to be changed.

279
00:28:36,570 --> 00:28:40,330
As it is, humanity has to be saved

280
00:28:40,490 --> 00:28:44,210
through you and nobody else.

281
00:28:44,930 --> 00:28:48,970
No president, no prime minister,

282
00:28:49,130 --> 00:28:51,410
no minister,

283
00:28:51,570 --> 00:28:55,370
none of these people can change the world

284
00:28:55,530 --> 00:28:57,290
and save it.

285
00:28:57,450 --> 00:29:00,370
It is you who are entitled.

286
00:29:00,530 --> 00:29:02,970
You have got this power.

287
00:29:03,170 --> 00:29:09,930
Do you realise your own status?

288
00:29:10,090 --> 00:29:14,730
Your own being?

289
00:29:14,890 --> 00:29:18,450
which has risen so high?

290
00:29:18,610 --> 00:29:24,490
It is not there. If that realisation is there,

291
00:29:24,650 --> 00:29:28,490
you would go all out

292
00:29:29,050 --> 00:29:35,610
to express your love and compassion to other people,

293
00:29:35,770 --> 00:29:41,010
to make them realise what they are.

294
00:29:41,170 --> 00:29:44,250
Only with Sahaja Yoga you can save this world.

295
00:29:44,410 --> 00:29:46,690
There's no other way out.

296
00:29:46,850 --> 00:29:53,570
Whatever you may try, say, to help the poor, to help this and that

297
00:29:53,730 --> 00:29:58,170
is something very, very superficial.

298
00:29:58,850 --> 00:30:06,450
Best thing is to give Realisation to every person you see.

299
00:30:08,090 --> 00:30:12,010
We have seen children. They're coming up.

300
00:30:12,170 --> 00:30:16,850
They'll be great Sahaja Yogis also. I can see that.

301
00:30:17,010 --> 00:30:23,090
But before them, you have to show your own merits

302
00:30:23,250 --> 00:30:26,130
of what you have done.

303
00:30:26,290 --> 00:30:29,210
It's not a static work.

304
00:30:29,370 --> 00:30:35,770
It's a big movement, which has to be really explosive

305
00:30:35,930 --> 00:30:45,290
and unless and until such a great step is taken,

306
00:30:49,690 --> 00:30:58,290
I don't know who will be blamed for the doomsday.

307
00:31:00,210 --> 00:31:05,650
You are the one[s] who have to build up

308
00:31:05,810 --> 00:31:09,410
the destiny of human beings.

309
00:31:09,570 --> 00:31:14,290
Don't consider as yourself, as something nothing.

310
00:31:14,450 --> 00:31:16,930
You could never have got your Realisation.

311
00:31:17,090 --> 00:31:19,170
You'd never have come to Me.

312
00:31:19,330 --> 00:31:23,650
Among so many, you are the ones who came to Me

313
00:31:23,810 --> 00:31:27,930
and who asked for Realisation and got it.

314
00:31:28,090 --> 00:31:31,010
You know it cannot be forced.

315
00:31:31,170 --> 00:31:34,810
This Realisation cannot be forced.

316
00:31:34,970 --> 00:31:38,130
This awareness cannot be forced.

317
00:31:38,290 --> 00:31:45,330
And the growthof this awareness also cannot be forced.

318
00:31:45,490 --> 00:31:51,890
You have to develop that attention deep down within yourself.

319
00:31:52,050 --> 00:31:56,490
And see for yourself what you have done,

320
00:31:56,650 --> 00:31:58,810
what you have done.

321
00:31:58,970 --> 00:32:05,210
If you are still busy with the money problem or the power problem

322
00:32:05,370 --> 00:32:09,770
and this problem and that, you are a problem.

323
00:32:09,930 --> 00:32:12,330
You are not a Sahaja Yogi.

324
00:32:12,490 --> 00:32:16,530
Sahaja Yogi is above everything else

325
00:32:16,690 --> 00:32:20,290
and is very powerful.

326
00:32:20,450 --> 00:32:25,010
Power will be achieved by them

327
00:32:25,170 --> 00:32:27,850
— power of love and compassion,

328
00:32:28,010 --> 00:32:32,250
which is not only words of love.

329
00:32:32,410 --> 00:32:38,010
It is not only act of loving others,

330
00:32:38,650 --> 00:32:47,370
but it is a powerful personality that you will have,

331
00:32:47,530 --> 00:32:50,970
which will just emit

332
00:32:51,130 --> 00:33:01,450
that great Divine Light and can capture people.

333
00:33:02,210 --> 00:33:13,090
All should just take a very brave personality.

334
00:33:14,450 --> 00:33:17,170
I must say people have improved,

335
00:33:17,330 --> 00:33:20,450
otherwise everybody used to write to Me:

336
00:33:20,610 --> 00:33:24,770
'This is wrong with me and that is wrong with my father.

337
00:33:24,930 --> 00:33:29,330
That is wrong with my great-grandmother' and all kinds of things.

338
00:33:29,490 --> 00:33:35,130
That is over now. Much less, I must say, much less.

339
00:33:35,850 --> 00:33:42,970
But instead of telling Me about people who are sick,

340
00:33:43,130 --> 00:33:46,490
people who have failed,

341
00:33:46,650 --> 00:33:54,450
people who are still in a state

342
00:33:55,090 --> 00:34:01,730
that cannot be improved, attention should be changed.

343
00:34:01,890 --> 00:34:08,010
If there's one person who has got cancer anywhere,

344
00:34:08,330 --> 00:34:12,250
immediately at least ten photographs will come to Me.

345
00:34:12,410 --> 00:34:15,850
Leader will write to Me. The wife's leader will write to Me.

346
00:34:16,010 --> 00:34:21,930
Everybody will write to Me that Mother, say such-and-such thing.

347
00:34:24,290 --> 00:34:30,570
Why? Is that My job?

348
00:34:30,730 --> 00:34:34,930
That person can be cured — we have hospitals —

349
00:34:35,090 --> 00:34:38,370
can be cured by photographs,

350
00:34:38,530 --> 00:34:43,690
but attention always goes now to compassion part.

351
00:34:43,850 --> 00:34:49,250
To those people who are so-called suffering physically,

352
00:34:49,410 --> 00:34:54,010
mentally, emotionally, financially,

353
00:34:54,210 --> 00:34:57,090
also in the marriages,

354
00:35:00,090 --> 00:35:03,090
that's not your job,

355
00:35:03,250 --> 00:35:06,050
neither Mine.

356
00:35:06,210 --> 00:35:10,370
If they're sick, they should take a photograph and work it out.

357
00:35:10,530 --> 00:35:14,970
If it doesn't work, that means that it doesn't deserve.

358
00:35:17,570 --> 00:35:24,810
There is no need for you to treat them and to work it out and,

359
00:35:24,970 --> 00:35:27,850
if it fails, to write to Me

360
00:35:28,010 --> 00:35:31,450
that 'Mother, such-and-such person is sick.'

361
00:35:31,610 --> 00:35:34,490
What's so important?

362
00:35:35,290 --> 00:35:41,330
Already we have so many healthy people going round.

363
00:35:41,490 --> 00:35:43,690
Why not use them first?

364
00:35:43,850 --> 00:35:48,010
Our job is not to cure people.

365
00:35:48,210 --> 00:35:53,050
Affection is all right. Compassion is all right. Is a natural thing

366
00:35:53,210 --> 00:35:59,930
that our attention goes to sick people or to the poor people

367
00:36:00,090 --> 00:36:04,570
or to the people who are suffering,

368
00:36:04,730 --> 00:36:10,010
but what about Sahaj Yog?

369
00:36:13,370 --> 00:36:16,650
If you have one sick person,

370
00:36:16,810 --> 00:36:20,930
hundred Sahaja Yogis will get after that.

371
00:36:21,090 --> 00:36:24,330
What is the reason?

372
00:36:24,490 --> 00:36:28,410
Is it compassion?

373
00:36:28,570 --> 00:36:30,770
It's not.

374
00:36:32,490 --> 00:36:39,050
They want to prove that they can cure that person.

375
00:36:40,010 --> 00:36:42,930
Is not compassion.

376
00:36:43,090 --> 00:36:46,370
Compassion today is

377
00:36:46,530 --> 00:36:52,890
to transform human beings into Sahajis,

378
00:36:53,290 --> 00:36:56,690
into good people.

379
00:36:56,850 --> 00:37:00,930
That is the love of Adi Shakti.

380
00:37:01,410 --> 00:37:05,170
Because those who are born have to die in any case.

381
00:37:05,330 --> 00:37:09,490
We should not be unkind, of course, but

382
00:37:09,650 --> 00:37:15,970
our attention should be how many people we are giving Realisation.

383
00:37:16,410 --> 00:37:19,370
Is a very common thing

384
00:37:19,530 --> 00:37:25,130
that people indulge more into so-called curing

385
00:37:25,290 --> 00:37:30,850
and improving and this. It's all right.

386
00:37:31,210 --> 00:37:36,410
Also there are problems like in the marriages, you see.

387
00:37:36,570 --> 00:37:39,850
Some marriage couple don't want to be there.

388
00:37:40,010 --> 00:37:43,450
It's all right. Finish them.

389
00:37:44,410 --> 00:37:48,570
If they don't want to live together, let them.

390
00:37:49,290 --> 00:37:53,010
We have many people who are sensible in this world,

391
00:37:53,170 --> 00:37:56,970
many people who are healthy in this world.

392
00:37:57,650 --> 00:38:00,490
Now how can you go on struggling with people

393
00:38:00,650 --> 00:38:04,530
who don't want to live together and have problems?

394
00:38:05,250 --> 00:38:07,810
That's not your job.

395
00:38:07,970 --> 00:38:11,050
First of all, you are a spiritual worker.

396
00:38:11,210 --> 00:38:14,370
You are not a social worker.

397
00:38:14,530 --> 00:38:16,090
Of course,

398
00:38:16,250 --> 00:38:21,610
by the way, you can do social work. It doesn't matter, by the way.

399
00:38:23,330 --> 00:38:29,370
But the main thing for you is to transform human beings.

400
00:38:30,050 --> 00:38:34,810
With that, the greatest disease

401
00:38:34,970 --> 00:38:40,650
is of meanness, of cruelty,

402
00:38:43,170 --> 00:38:48,770
of torturing others, anger.

403
00:38:49,730 --> 00:38:53,450
All these diseases can be cured,

404
00:38:53,610 --> 00:38:57,650
which are internal, not external.

405
00:38:58,090 --> 00:39:00,370
That is today wanted.

406
00:39:00,530 --> 00:39:04,530
Every country's fighting and is tortured

407
00:39:04,690 --> 00:39:11,850
and is in peril all the time of getting destroyed.

408
00:39:12,810 --> 00:39:18,130
The only way you can do it is to give them Realisation.

409
00:39:18,290 --> 00:39:22,890
Now what happens is to be seen very clearly

410
00:39:23,690 --> 00:39:29,130
that when you give Realisation to someone

411
00:39:29,290 --> 00:39:34,810
and he values it, and he grows into it,

412
00:39:35,010 --> 00:39:39,490
then you are protected.

413
00:39:39,650 --> 00:39:43,490
You are completely protected.

414
00:39:44,050 --> 00:39:47,850
Who protects you, you may say?

415
00:39:48,010 --> 00:39:50,930
The Adi Shakti, all right,

416
00:39:51,090 --> 00:39:58,730
but also there is a destructive power working in this world,

417
00:39:58,890 --> 00:40:05,570
not of negativity, but positive destructive power of Shiva.

418
00:40:06,130 --> 00:40:17,650
If He says that if Adi Shakti's work is going on well, He's happy.

419
00:40:17,930 --> 00:40:21,690
But He's sitting there and watching each and every person,

420
00:40:21,850 --> 00:40:25,530
each and every work of Sahaja Yogis

421
00:40:25,690 --> 00:40:34,010
and if He finds something really very wrong,

422
00:40:34,210 --> 00:40:37,770
I cannot control it.

423
00:40:38,010 --> 00:40:44,530
He destroys. I cannot go to that point.

424
00:40:45,330 --> 00:40:48,330
He destroys.

425
00:40:48,490 --> 00:40:56,210
Not only destroys, but thousands He can destroy.

426
00:40:59,970 --> 00:41:03,810
Anywhere there is a calamity,

427
00:41:03,970 --> 00:41:10,970
we can say, like an earthquake

428
00:41:11,130 --> 00:41:15,650
or some sort of a hurricane,

429
00:41:15,810 --> 00:41:17,650
all these things come

430
00:41:17,810 --> 00:41:25,690
through the working of Shri Mahadeva.

431
00:41:26,930 --> 00:41:30,290
I can't help you there,

432
00:41:30,730 --> 00:41:36,130
but if you really give Realisation to people,

433
00:41:37,850 --> 00:41:41,490
all these can be averted.

434
00:41:42,410 --> 00:41:48,450
Of course, it is the whim, I should say, of Adi Shakti

435
00:41:48,610 --> 00:41:53,010
that She started this work of creating this world,

436
00:41:53,170 --> 00:41:58,330
of creating you and making you Sahaja Yogis,

437
00:41:58,530 --> 00:42:02,850
but your responsibility is also very important.

438
00:42:06,050 --> 00:42:09,730
You cannot be responsible.

439
00:42:12,570 --> 00:42:22,450
Maybe it was, I felt, My responsibility, but there's a difference.

440
00:42:24,210 --> 00:42:28,650
I never felt it was My responsibility,

441
00:42:29,730 --> 00:42:33,610
never felt this was My job,

442
00:42:33,770 --> 00:42:36,850
never felt I have to do it.

443
00:42:37,010 --> 00:42:39,490
'I did it.'

444
00:42:42,850 --> 00:42:44,810
That is the work.

445
00:42:44,970 --> 00:42:49,250
That's the kind of personality you should have.

446
00:42:49,410 --> 00:42:55,290
You have to do it in a very humble manner,

447
00:42:57,410 --> 00:43:01,930
in a very beautiful manner

448
00:43:02,090 --> 00:43:07,250
and you'll be amazed to see how you are protected,

449
00:43:07,410 --> 00:43:13,930
how you are supported and how everything works out.

450
00:43:14,210 --> 00:43:17,810
The greatest joy you will get when you will find

451
00:43:17,970 --> 00:43:21,050
you can give Realisation to people.

452
00:43:22,730 --> 00:43:26,290
You can change their lives.

453
00:43:26,970 --> 00:43:29,290
Never you would feel such joy,

454
00:43:29,450 --> 00:43:37,410
even if you get, say, a big lottery maybe,

455
00:43:37,930 --> 00:43:41,850
a big job or a big name

456
00:43:42,010 --> 00:43:48,450
or a very big award, no.

457
00:43:49,410 --> 00:43:54,610
The joy of creating Sahaja Yogis

458
00:43:55,450 --> 00:44:00,290
knows no bounds,

459
00:44:00,890 --> 00:44:04,770
is such a joy-giving thing.

460
00:44:05,850 --> 00:44:10,850
You develop such fraternities,

461
00:44:11,010 --> 00:44:17,050
such solidarity, as they call it, such oneness,

462
00:44:17,450 --> 00:44:22,290
such enjoyment of love,

463
00:44:22,730 --> 00:44:25,930
enjoyment of compassion.

464
00:44:26,090 --> 00:44:29,890
It's a different level of enjoyment

465
00:44:30,050 --> 00:44:34,130
that's not like ordinary enjoyments.

466
00:44:36,450 --> 00:44:39,850
You're not to be afraid of Me,

467
00:44:40,010 --> 00:44:44,250
but be afraid of yourself.

468
00:44:44,410 --> 00:44:48,130
Have a watch on yourself and see for yourself

469
00:44:48,290 --> 00:44:51,850
what have you been doing so far.

470
00:44:52,010 --> 00:44:55,250
What have you done so far?

471
00:44:55,410 --> 00:45:01,730
Because you have been enlightened.

472
00:45:02,490 --> 00:45:05,450
If the enlightened people

473
00:45:05,610 --> 00:45:09,450
cannot give light, what's the use in having them?

474
00:45:09,610 --> 00:45:12,370
Look at these little, little candles.

475
00:45:12,530 --> 00:45:18,290
Whatever little light they have, they're giving that light.

476
00:45:18,450 --> 00:45:22,410
They're burning themselves to give that light.

477
00:45:22,570 --> 00:45:28,650
If we cannot give that light,

478
00:45:29,930 --> 00:45:34,210
what is the use of enlightenment?

479
00:45:35,370 --> 00:45:40,090
Enlightened doesn't mean the light for yourself only

480
00:45:40,250 --> 00:45:45,130
the light of love, compassion,

481
00:45:45,290 --> 00:45:52,010
which is divine, which is not normal, which is not ordinary,

482
00:45:52,170 --> 00:45:54,930
as you see in the films.

483
00:45:55,090 --> 00:46:00,450
It is a divine love which works

484
00:46:01,650 --> 00:46:06,690
and that is what makes Me sometimes little weak

485
00:46:06,850 --> 00:46:10,250
when I hear that Sahaja Yogis now

486
00:46:10,410 --> 00:46:14,970
are getting involved in money, in cheating.

487
00:46:15,130 --> 00:46:19,690
I mean, all kinds of criminal activities they do.

488
00:46:19,850 --> 00:46:23,610
I can't understand. I can't believe it.

489
00:46:23,770 --> 00:46:27,730
After getting the highest,

490
00:46:27,890 --> 00:46:33,730
why do you want to go so low as that?

491
00:46:33,890 --> 00:46:39,570
Because you have not yet felt what you have got.

492
00:46:41,130 --> 00:46:45,370
You have not realised what you have got.

493
00:46:47,570 --> 00:46:51,250
And you don't respect yourself.

494
00:46:51,650 --> 00:46:58,610
Still, if you are on the same line and the same level,

495
00:46:58,770 --> 00:47:09,490
I must say you have done no justice to Me or to yourself.

496
00:47:10,010 --> 00:47:13,570
We have to work it out.

497
00:47:13,730 --> 00:47:17,210
Single-handed, I've done it,

498
00:47:17,370 --> 00:47:20,970
worked very hard, I must say,

499
00:47:21,130 --> 00:47:28,290
in the sense that I had to deal with horrible people,

500
00:47:29,810 --> 00:47:37,010
very unkind, very selfish, very cruel.

501
00:47:37,770 --> 00:47:40,730
That doesn't matter.

502
00:47:43,130 --> 00:47:47,170
And such beautiful pearls I have discovered.

503
00:47:47,810 --> 00:47:52,490
But you must keep your lustre

504
00:47:52,650 --> 00:47:55,530
and work it out.

505
00:47:55,690 --> 00:48:02,570
I'll be very happy to know that Sahaja Yoga is spreading

506
00:48:02,730 --> 00:48:07,370
with leaps and bounds, with great speed

507
00:48:07,530 --> 00:48:11,250
and that people are really

508
00:48:11,410 --> 00:48:19,330
getting into that realm

509
00:48:19,850 --> 00:48:26,770
of peace, joy and happiness.

510
00:48:26,930 --> 00:48:29,730
That's My dream

511
00:48:29,890 --> 00:48:33,850
and I hope you all will all work it out.

512
00:48:34,290 --> 00:48:36,970
Thank you very much.

